!groups/global/knowledge-base/
groups/global/CLAUDE.md
# Telegram main - track everything except credentials and logs
groups/telegram_main/credentials/
groups/telegram_main/logs/

# Secrets
*.keys.json
.env

# Temp files
.tmp-*

